{"tid":1995314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋喺五週年前一日分咗手","createTime":"2020-04-30T07:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T13:03:14.000Z","uid":209310,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"218e31091ccb25670b64c70eb457c1db8b12fd38","tid":1995314,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"其實我預咗會有呢一日。<br />\n不過我冇諗過會咁諷刺，係五週年前一日。哈哈。<br />\n知道會有呢日，但其實我乜都冇準備。<br />\n<br />\n猝不及防。<br />\n砰&mdash;<br />\n一下重擊，好撚痛。<br />\n<br />\n如果我有八十年命，扣翻十歲前同六十歲打後，有五十年。<br />\n原來你佔咗我人生嘅十份之一。<br />\n準確啲講，我嘥咗你十份一人生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者由一開始就係錯。我嘅性格已經提前註定咗呢段感情嘅失敗。我覺得你喺我身邊係天經地義嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n我愛你，但我冇珍惜。<br />\n<br />\n對唔住。<br />\n<br />\n我想將全部嘅溫柔俾你。<br />\n但係咪已經太遲？<br />\n<br />\n我已經失去咗你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我飲到好醉&mdash; 點解我連你個樣都唔記得？<br />\n我係咪太習慣將所有嘢當做理所應得？<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅世界一早已經冇得分開。<br />\n你嘅朋友<br />\n我嘅朋友<br />\n你屋企人<br />\n我屋企人<br />\n<br />\n一直都覺得你唔可以冇咗我，但點解反而好似變咗我唔可以冇咗你？<br />\n定呢個世界根本冇話邊個冇咗邊個就唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你會瘋狂喊一排。<br />\n你會覺得世界上再冇愛情。<br />\n你會搵個新男朋友。<br />\n<br />\n你會發覺<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>咦，點解條友咁撚似佢？</em></span><br />\n<br />\n你會分手。<br />\n你會再搵個新男朋友。<br />\n你會慢慢忘記我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好想知佢對你好唔好。<br />\n我已經再冇資格知邊個對你好唔好。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: maroon;\">等待著你說我不是你的誰 誰說我沒有準備</span></em>"},{"pid":"a50acfbe432dfd27355964886ed60dfd1373e5ad","tid":1995314,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"a01e7bae2841bfa7e7d96a060fb50cc5bd400c4a","tid":1995314,"uid":209310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a50acfbe432dfd27355964886ed60dfd1373e5ad","tid":1995314,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fde2501adc91af646810d7a687578606a3746e","tid":1995314,"uid":235535,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"其實分手好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49954e1bb8ee2f9c31232e8bf982d52fc1c865d","tid":1995314,"uid":209310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40fde2501adc91af646810d7a687578606a3746e","tid":1995314,"uid":235535,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"其實分手好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"過咗好耐睇緊係小事 有咩時間沖唔淡"},{"pid":"dfe29a26bc1dd988a7d0144e036fc522096b84ef","tid":1995314,"uid":235535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d49954e1bb8ee2f9c31232e8bf982d52fc1c865d","tid":1995314,"uid":209310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40fde2501adc91af646810d7a687578606a3746e","tid":1995314,"uid":235535,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"其實分手好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"過咗好耐睇緊係小事 有咩時間沖唔淡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"換個心態去諗分手依件事會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b44c86af38e50ee2f2fd4e2632ada1c72febd6e","tid":1995314,"uid":41960,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"香港地媾女易到仆街，唔駛唔開心。"},{"pid":"b84f642d0b84a12d07e023af79dc76d27008d41c","tid":1995314,"uid":177512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b44c86af38e50ee2f2fd4e2632ada1c72febd6e","tid":1995314,"uid":41960,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"香港地媾女易到仆街，唔駛唔開心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"照下鏡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal